底？"},{"pid":"a336b99fb58c29fa0d60258055c4d28e3f934479","tid":2508000,"uid":142964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"呢d 正一仆街垃圾青輕人黎，做臭自己個個generation"},{"pid":"8492ca1d6c468dc65255fbae3ed562f99c06b654","tid":2508000,"uid":203050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"以為道歉就冇事？快d告佢地 呢d慣犯依家呃飲呃食 放過佢地既話遲d穿櫃桶底<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543a37e18718daa87f0782be9d8c7c60bd0b8b7c","tid":2508000,"uid":126382,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"講撚咗90、00後唔係單非就雙非<br />\n<br />\n支那人就梗係支那人正常發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港？ 屌你老母香港新一代都已經唔係香港人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班垃圾仲要讀咁多書，屌你老母正宗讀屎片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df61123f995e861b281aaddf7f8a5e2db2f2ade5","tid":2508000,"uid":126382,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4fe591edfdc6f033c1c6801ef46790ba2aae668","tid":2508000,"ui